
Overview of noun shimmy

The noun shimmy has 3 senses (no senses from tagged texts)
                                       
1. shimmy -- (an abnormal wobble in a motor vehicle (especially in the front wheels); "he could feel the shimmy in the steering wheel")
2. chemise, shimmy, shift, slip, teddy -- (a woman's sleeveless undergarment)
3. shimmy -- (lively dancing (usually to ragtime music) with much shaking of the shoulders and hips)

